      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "It&#39;s worth noting that this &quot;SAM Interface&quot; is actually called a &quot;Functional Interface&quot; and that looking at the <code>Comparator</code> documentation we can see that it&#39;s decorated with the annotation <code>@FunctionalInterface</code>. This decorator is the magic that allows <code>Integer::max</code> and <code>Integer::min</code> to be converted into a <code>Comparator</code>."
