    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I had an error with an array getting the max and the min so my solution was:</p>\n\n<pre><code>int max = Arrays.stream(arrayWithInts).max().getAsInt();\nint min = Arrays.stream(arrayWithInts).min().getAsInt();\n</code></pre>\n"
